msgid "Scenario II: Return to The Doom of Eztli"
msgstr "冒险II：重返埃兹特里的覆灭"

msgid "Remove the original Burial Pit, Underground Ruins, Secret Passage locations from the game."
msgstr "将原版的坑葬墓室、地下遗迹和秘密通道地点从游戏中移除。"

msgid "Replace the original Entryway, Ancient Hall, Grand Chamber, and Chamber of Time locations with the new versions from <i>The Return to The Doom of Eztli</i> encounter set."
msgstr "用<i>重返埃兹特里的覆灭</i>遭遇组的新版地点替换原版的遗迹入口、古代石厅、华美石室和时间石室地点。"

msgid "Replace the original Harbinger of Valusia enemy with the new Harbinger of Valusia <i>(The Sleeper Returns)</i>."
msgstr "用新版的瓦卢西亚的预示者<i>(沉睡者归来))</i>敌人替换原版的瓦卢西亚的预示者。"

msgid "Create the exploration deck. This is done by taking Sealed Passage, Mosaic Chamber, Tomb of the Ancients, Throne Room, Snake Pit, Ancient Hall, and Grand Chamber and shuffling them together. Do not include any encounter cards listed in the original setup instructions."
msgstr "构建探索牌堆。将封印通道、彩砖石室、古代墓穴、王座大厅、蛇洞、古代石厅和华美石室混洗形成探索牌堆，不要加入原版的冒险设置指示中列出的其他遭遇卡。"

msgid "Set the following cards aside, out of play: The Harbinger of Valusia enemy, the 3 Pit Viper cards from the <i>Serpents</i> encounter set, and the Chamber of Time location, and the Relic of Ages asset."
msgstr "将下列卡牌放在一边，位于场外：瓦卢西亚的预示者敌人卡、从<i>蛇族</i>遭遇组中找出的3张蝮蛇卡牌、时间石室地点卡、古代遗物支援卡。"

msgid "Which investigator should add the \"Mysterious Scepter\" to their supplies?"
msgstr "要在哪位调查员的补给品中记录“神秘权杖”？"

msgid "Mysterious Scepter"
msgstr "神秘权杖"

msgid "A mysterious scepter you found in the throne room."
msgstr "你在王座大厅里找到的神秘权杖。"

msgid "The investigators must replay <b>Scenario II: Return to The Doom of Eztli</b>. Reset the game to this scenario’s Setup. Do not record anything in your Campaign Log except for any trauma suffered from your previous game. No experience points are earned from your previous game."
msgstr "调查员必须重玩<b>冒险II：重返埃兹特里的覆灭</b>。重置游戏至本场冒险的<b>设置阶段</b>。除了在上一局游戏中受到的任何创伤以外，不要在冒险日志记录其他任何信息。你们在上一局游戏不获得经验点数。"
